Pluxee – Your Benefits, Made Simple
Discover a smarter way to enjoy your employee benefits with the Pluxee app.
Check your balance, track your spending in real-time, and find new places to enjoy your benefits — all in one simple, secure app.
What You Can Do with Pluxee:

- Check Your Balance Anytime
Stay on top of your spending with real-time updates on your balance and transactions.
-  Discover Nearby Places

Find partner locations near you where you can use your benefits — from restaurants to retail.

- Pay with Ease
Use Apple Pay or Google Pay to make fast, secure payments directly from your phone.

- Get Exclusive Offers
Unlock special deals and make your benefits go even further.
- Enjoy a Seamless Experience

One app, all your benefits — designed to be fast, safe, and easy to use.
- Love the app? Let us know!

Your feedback helps us keep improving. Rate and review the app and help us shape the future of your Pluxee experience.

Представямe Ви приложението Pluxee

Открийте свят на възможности с новото приложение Pluxee! Използвайте социалните си придобивки в интуитивна и сигурна платформа. Следете баланса и трансакциите си и открийте нови вълнуващи места около Вас. Да започваме!

Основни функции:

Удобно, сигурно и многофункционално:

Приложението Pluxee предлага отлично и сигурно потребителско изживяване. Вземете най-доброто от Pluxee в едно приложение.

Баланс и трансакции в реално време:

Получавате в реално време информация за Вашите баланси и трансакции, по всяко време и навсякъде. Край на изненадите - винаги ще знаете с какви средства разполагате.

Открийте нови места:

Получете повече от това, което наистина има значение и с едно натискане на бутон вижте къде може да пазарувате с Вашата карта.

Насладете се на изживяването с Pluxee още днес:

Изтеглете приложението Pluxee и открийте свят на възможности. Извлечете максимума от допълнителните си социални придобивките и се насладете на това, което е наистина важно за Вас.

Вашето мнение е от значение:

Ние ценим Вашата обратната връзка. Моля, оценете приложението Pluxee. Вашето мнение ни помага да подобрим клиентското изживяване и да ви предоставим най-доброто обслужване.

It's Possible.

Quickly and easily connect and control your smart home devices through SmartThings.
SmartThings is compatible with 100s of smart home brands. So you can control all of your smart home gadgets in one place, including your Samsung Smart TV and smart home appliances.
With SmartThings, you can connect, monitor and control multiple smart home devices quicker and easier. Connect your Samsung smart TVs, smart appliances, smart speakers and brands like Ring, Nest and Philips Hue - all from one app.
Then control your smart devices using voice assistants including Google Assistant

[Key Features]
- Control and check in on your home from wherever you are
- Connect your smart devices across many different brands to work together by setting ‘scenes’
- Build routines that are set on time, weather, and device status, so your home runs smoothly in the background
- Allow shared control by giving access to other users
- Receive status updates about your devices with automated notifications
- Talk to your devices using Google Assistant
- Track, monitor and save money on energy with SmartThings Energy. See how much your home and compatible Samsung devices cost to run, and try various energy saving features, such as AI saving mode, or schedule devices to run during off peak hours.
- Receive recipe recommendations by scanning meal kits, wine, and meat. Plan, shop and prep meals with the help of SmartThings Cooking 

※ Some features may not be available in all countries.

[App requirements]
Some mobile devices may not be supported.
- iOS 16.0 or later / iPhone 6s or later / iPad mini 4 or later

※ App permissions
The following permissions are required for the app service. For optional permissions, the default functionality of the service is turned on, but not allowed. 

[Required access permissions]
-
 
[Optional access permissions]
• Bluetooth: to find nearby devices using Bluetooth or BLE
• Microphone: Used to set up ultrasonic sensor-equipped devices
• Camera: Scan QR codes.
• Location: to automate actions using GPS (GPS optional)
                    Used to find Wi-Fi information to add devices with iOS 13 or later versions
• Contacts: Used to verify user information that will be used when sending text messages

Floorcare
Enjoy effortless home cleaning with the Dyson robot or a cordless vacuum.

-	Schedule and track cleans, choose modes for each room, and set areas to avoid for your robot.
-	Learn how much dust your robot has removed and view scientific proof of a deep clean.
-	Access step-by-step guides for setup, troubleshooting, and maintenance to keep your Dyson cordless vacuum and wet floor cleaner in top condition.

Compatible with a wide range of Dyson floor care machines, including the Dyson 360 Vis Nav™ robot vacuum, V15™, V8™, V12™, Gen5detect™ vacuum cleaners, and the Wash G1™ wet cleaner.

Air treatment
Manage your Dyson air purifier, humidifier, and fan to take control of the air quality around you.

-	Control airflow speed, oscillation, Auto mode, Sleep timer, temperature, and humidity remotely.
-	Monitor air quality data to track your exposure to pollutants.
-	Gain insights into your home environment with monthly air quality reports.
-	Track filter life and receive alerts, to easily order replacements, ensuring your machine performs at its best.

Compatible with a wide range of Dyson purifiers, purifying fan heaters, purifying fans, and purifying humidifiers.

Hair care
Get the best out of your Dyson hair care device with the MyDyson™ app – your must-have companion for effortless and elevated styling.

-	Watch our styling guides to achieve your desired look with your hair dryer, multi-styler, and straightener.
-	Create your hair profile to get the best results with i.d. curl™ and for tailored content.
-	Set up your personalised curling routine to create perfect curls with your Airwrap i.d.™.
-	Elevate your skills with insider tips from celebrity stylists and our Beauty experts.

Connected features, such as i.d. curl™, are available with Airwrap i.d.™. The app also supports styling guides, tailored content, and hair profile for both Airwrap i.d™ and non-connected devices: Airwrap™, Supersonic™, Airstrait™, and Corrale™.

Audio
Get the app to enjoy the best audio experience with your Dyson headphones.
-	Cycle between Isolation mode, Transparency mode noise, and Off.
-	Choose from three equaliser presets to get your perfect sound.
-	Track your sound exposure or enable the safe volume limiter to look after your hearing.
-	Discover the full range of ear cushions and outer caps for your Dyson OnTrac™ headphones.

Compatible with Dyson OnTrac™ and Dyson Zone™ headphones.

Lighting
Transform your space with intelligent lighting that adapts to your lifestyle.

-	Adjust brightness and colour temperature settings to create your perfect environment.
-	Select a preset mode – Relax, Study, and Precision – to match your task, mood, or time of the day.
-	Set timers and schedules to automatically turn lights on or off.
-	Elevate your skills with insider tips from celebrity stylists and our Beauty experts.

Compatible with Dyson Solarcycle Morph™ desk and Dyson Solarcycle Morph™ floor.

More features

Build your smart home
Connect your Dyson product with Siri, Alexa, and Google Home for seamless integration.*

Get help
Speak to a Dyson Expert, explore user guides, and solve issues with our troubleshooting tool.

Be the first to find out
Get notified about special offers, launches, and events before anyone else.

Please note, some Dyson machines require a 2.4GHz Wi-Fi connection. Please check specific connection requirements on the Dyson website.
If you have any comments you’d like to share on the latest release, you can contact us directly at askdyson@dyson.co.uk.

*The functionality of Alexa, Siri, and Google Home may vary depending on the country and product.

Set up, manage, and control Tapo home security cameras, smart plugs, smart lighting, and more – all from the Tapo app. Tapo aims to help you live a smarter, easier, and more secure life.

Roborock App is a dedicated application designed to control Roborock’s smart hardware devices. 
It supports network-enabled products in Roborock’s robotic vacuum cleaners, wet and dry vacuum cleaners, and molecular sieve-based washer dryers.
You can remotely control smart devices and check their status and cleaning progress through this app anytime, anywhere.
Easily unlock more advanced features through the Roborock app.

【Roborock Robotic Vacuum Cleaner】
· Check the cleaning map and path anywhere and anytime you want, and control the cleaning progress in real-time. 
· Choose from various personalized cleaning methods, including room cleaning, zone cleaning, scheduled cleaning, and spot cleaning routines.
· Set up frequently used cleaning tasks as routines for one-tap starts. 
· Choose multiple cleaning preferences, including Vacuum, Mop, Vac & Mop, SmartPlan (applicable to certain models only), and Customize mode. 
· Set up a personalized cleaning plan by adjusting suction power, water flow, cleaning frequency, and route (applicable to certain models only).
· Enables you to edit a map based on your home and set names for thresholds, carpets, floor types, furniture, and rooms. 
· Set up invisible walls and no-go zones and your robot will not cross or enter them during cleaning.
· Enjoy a variety of fun features, including remote viewing, obstacle photos, pet snapshots, cruise mode, pet search, and custom tones (applicable to select models only).

【Roborock Wet and Dry Vacuum Cleaner】
· Adjust water flow, suction power, roller speed, and detergent level (applicable to select models only) based on the floor and dirt level.
· Smart scheduled self-cleaning and drying: automatically initiates self-cleaning and drying based on historical operation records.

【Roborock Washer Dryer】
· Check the washing progress and operating status anywhere and anytime you want.
· Choose from over 20 smart washing and drying programs to meet the professional needs of various fabrics and clothing, ensuring optimal washing performance.
· Set one program as the App Program for quick access on the control panel.

【Permissions】
To provide certain services, you need to enable the relevant permissions on your mobile device. We will only need the relevant permissions and access your personal information (if relevant) when you use the relevant functions. For the optional permissions, you can refuse or withdraw these permissions at any time, for which you may not be able to use the corresponding services, but this will not affect other functions of the App. The current permissions that the app may need are as follows: 
· Location (Optional)
Accesses location information to connect to WiFi, find nearby devices ready for connection, and retrieve details about the current WiFi connection.
· Camera (Optional)
Enables the camera to scan QR codes for easier WiFi connection.
· Photos (Optional)
Allows access to photos for uploading profile pictures and attaching images when providing feedback. If your device supports features like downloading obstacle images, taking screenshots, or recording during remote viewing, photos and videos can be stored.
· Microphone (Optional)
Used for sound transmission on devices that support remote viewing.
· WLAN (Optional)
Facilitates connection to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices for communication and connectivity.
· Bluetooth (Optional)
Enables connection to Bluetooth signals from smart devices for communication and device connecting.
· Notifications (Optional)
Allows the app to send you device and system notifications.
· Local Network (Optional)
When connecting devices on the iOS local network, grants access to the local network to connect to WiFi networks emitted by smart devices.
· Siri & Search (Optional)
When opening Siri on iOS, interacts with Siri to control the starting and moving of devices based on the Routines set up in the mobile device.

MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

The dating app bringing people closer to love

Bumble is the dating app where people meet, make connections, and start their love stories. We believe meaningful relationships are the foundation of a happy, healthy life — and we're here to help you find yours with a commitment to member safety and tools that empower confident dating.

Match with the right people, date, and find meaningful connection

Bumble is a free app for meeting singles and building connections grounded in mutual respect and trust. Whether you’re ready to find the one or date for fun, Bumble can help you connect with real people to build something authentic.

As champions of love, we prioritize creating a space where our members feel respected, confident, and empowered to make connections

- Our members are at the heart of everything we do
- We put safety first — so you can date with confidence, knowing you’re connecting with verified matches
- Respect, courage, and joy guide how we show up — and inspire others to do the same

Try our free features — built to make dating easier
- For better connections, conversations, and dates, personalize your profile with interests and prompts to showcase who you are, what you’re into, and what you’re looking for
- Trust that the person you’re talking to is real with ID Verification
- Feel confident with expert-backed dating advice designed to help you succeed
- See what music you bond over by linking your Spotify account
- Video chat and share your favorite pictures with your matches to get to know them better
- Chat with peace of mind — knowing that when you’re talking to new people, all messages must meet our community guidelines
- Get extra reassurance by sharing the details of your meetups with someone you trust
- If you’re ever in need of a dating break, hide your profile with the Snooze Mode (you'll still keep all your matches)

Want even more ways to connect? Bumble Premium unlocks extra features to boost your dating experience
- See everyone who likes you
- Use Advanced Filters like “What are they looking for?” to meet people who share your values, hobbies, and goals
- Rematch with expired connections — so you don’t miss out on a great potential date
- Browse anonymously with Incognito Mode and only seen by who you want to see you
- Extend your matches by 24 hours
- Swipe as much as you like to meet more people
- Tap into dating scenes around the world with Travel Mode
- Stand out and get noticed with free SuperSwipes & Spotlights, refreshed weekly

Inclusivity is key
At Bumble, we promise to support and include all forms of love: straight, gay, lesbian, queer, and beyond. We want everyone in our community to feel safe and welcome. So no matter how you identify, if you're looking for a place to chat, date, and find real love, we’ve got what you’re looking for.

FEATURES:

◆ Online Secret Santa
Set up your Secret Santa gift exchange by creating a group, set a budget and date, add the names of friends, family and set exclusions. This app allows unlimited participants.

Easily set exclusions, selected participants will not be paired together.

This Secret Santa app requires no registration. Only one device is necessary to organise the draw.

The offline mode will set up your gift exchange on the spot, directly on the screen.

Each group member can add gift suggestions on their personal wish list.

None of the data you share with the app is shared with anyone else except the people involved. We do not store emails nor phone numbers, Santa hates SPAM anyway.

Happy Holidays,
Team SecretSanta

Control your smart kitchen and home appliances from Bosch, Siemens, NEFF, Gaggenau, and our other brands in a simple and convenient way – with the official app for BSH Home Appliances.

Download the Home Connect app now – it’s free!

Get the most out of your smart home appliances. Home Connect allows you to manage your household in a whole new way. Whenever you want, from wherever you are.

•	Control and monitor your kitchen and home appliances
•	Easier use of appliances – start & stop, select quick or silent options
•	Get helpful push notifications, e.g., when your programme has finished
•	Save time and energy by creating automations
•	Enable exclusive in-app features and download software updates for your appliances
•	Find recipes and endless cooking inspiration

Control and manage your smart appliances anytime, anywhere

Did I switch off the oven? Instead of heading back home to check, simply take a look at the app. You will see and be able to control the status of your appliances straight away with immediate access to important functionalities, whether at home or on the go.

Be aware of all that’s important

Oh, the fridge door has been left open? When do I need to descale the coffee machine? How often should I clean the oven? Important notifications and reminders regarding maintenance and care will be sent to you automatically. And even if things don’t go to plan: by using remote diagnostics our customer service team will help you resolve any issue. You can also simply check the manual which is conveniently stored in the app.

Voice-control your appliances via Amazon Alexa, or Google Home

Whether it’s making coffee, preheating the oven, or starting the washing machine: Voice your command and Amazon Alexa or Google Home will take care of the rest. What’s more, you can use predefined or individual routines for recurring tasks to orchestrate your smart home, like having your coffee made at the same time each working day.

Finding the best programme and other little helpers

Dishwasher, dryer, or oven – depending on the appliance and task at hand, you will be recommended the ideal programme and settings, whether it’s a pile of dirty dishes, a load of washing, or the cheesecake recipe for your next family reunion. Based on your feedback, programmes can even improve over time to better fit your needs. And with Coffee Playlist you can conveniently fulfil your guests’ coffee requests to match that cheesecake.

Let your oven do the work

Don’t want to keep checking whether your dish is ready? Simply set the desired browning level for the selected dish and start the oven. Artificial Intelligence evaluates the browning level based on images taken by the integrated camera. The oven switches off as soon as the selected level is reached. The camera also lets you check your dish from anywhere on your smartphone.
 
Do you have any questions or feedback? Drop us a message at info.uk@home-connect.com, we’re happy to hear from you.

PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries.

Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space.

Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates!

* HOW PURE WORKS?
Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing.

* IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN
Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe.  

* WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE
Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery.

* OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE
Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. 
Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. 

PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside.
Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions:

- If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.
- All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations.
- Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase.
- All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy
